"repr. Defaults to ``numpy.get_printoptions()['threshold']``."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../../../../.conda/lib/python3.13/site-packages/numpy/__init__.py:docstring
#: of numpy.array2string:76
msgid "**edgeitems**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../../../../.conda/lib/python3.13/site-packages/numpy/__init__.py:docstring
